	"name": "Wildlord",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/nature/stealth-hide-eyes-green.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are far more at home in wild, untamed places than anywhere else, and the denizens of the wilds welcome you as their own. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Strength, Dexterity, Constitution, or Wisdom score increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die with the Survival skill. Your maximum expertise die for Survival becomes a d12.</p></li><li><p>Your speed increases by 5 feet.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with your choice of two of the following languages: Elvish, Gnomish, Primordial, and Sylvan.</p></li><li><p>Choose one of the following options:</p><ul><li><p>You learn a druid cantrip of your choice.</p></li><li><p>You are continuously under the effects of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.z5a26lxyh3esw2rl]{speak with animals}.</p></li><li><p>You are continuously under the effects of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.rek0fg987gg30wp9]{speak with plants}.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p>Once you have selected this feat, you can no longer gain levels in classes other than ranger.</p>",
